Body:
Description: Good morning team,
I'm working for a French company named Socomec.
We purchased Pingcastle Pro licence through a partner, Athéo Ingénierie, but we don't understand how to download the MSI package.
Can you please tell us how to do ? 
Thank you.

Product Downloads are available through our customer portal.

 

An employee of Socomec must register on Netwrix.com/support in order to access the installation and license files.

 

ATHEO Ongenierie is a partner, the ticket details must be updated to show ATHEO as the partner account and Socomec as the account name
What We've Learned Updated: Customer wants to locate installation files for PingCastle

Next Steps Updated: First, i attached the installation file but it doesn't work this way. Advised by Brandon to refer them over to the Netwrix.com/support website and register as SOCOMEC to access those files.
